2026-06-29
- Propagated a per-request X-Request-ID end-to-end; every v2 error body now
  carries a request_id (also on the X-Request-ID response header) for log
  correlation, and the id is forwarded to the connector.
- Reverted the BPMN builder to a pure translator: dropped the graph/referential
  validation and content-rewriting normalizers. invalid_model is now only a
  crash-safety net, raised for a reply that is not valid JSON or whose graph is
  malformed enough to fail during build -- not for general structural checks.
- Brought the PNML layouter to full textbook-grade Sugiyama: overlap-free
  placement, straightened spine, and explicit arc waypoints for rework-loop
  back-edges and multi-layer arcs.
- Skipped the unused BPMN layout on the PNML path; marked the PNML source place
  with an initial token and showed the exclusive-gateway X marker in laid-out
  BPMN.
- Documented that /v2/generate/* relays the connector's 422 model_unprocessable
  (with details) and 429 upstream_error responses unchanged.
- Raised the connector HTTP timeout 60s -> 180s so slow reasoning models finish
  before the client gives up; fixed Swagger docs behind the reverse-proxy prefix.
- Applied security dependency bumps and bumped the service to 2.2.0.

2026-06-08
- Introduced the versioned /v2 API: /v2/generate/bpmn, /v2/generate/pnml,
  /v2/models, and /v2/health.
- Moved the provider key out of the JSON body to bearer auth
  (Authorization: Bearer <api_key>) on /v2/generate/*.
- Made the connector the authoritative validator for the generate contract;
  T2P forwards the request verbatim and relays the connector's responses
  (including 4xx) instead of duplicating validation.
- Added the ConnectorClient transport seam for the LLM API connector and
  replaced the old direct-provider pipeline.
- Defined the connector boundary as a structured JSON process model; T2P now
  verifies the model's referential integrity and converts it to BPMN XML,
  returning invalid_model on a structurally broken reply.
- Added a layered layout for the generated BPMN and assigned layout
  coordinates to the PNML produced by /v2/generate/pnml.
- Standardized v2 error responses to { "error": { "code", "message" } }.
- Deprecated the unversioned generation endpoints (functional until
  2026-12-01) with Deprecation/Sunset/Link headers; /api_call now returns
  410 Gone after its 2025-12-31 sunset.
- Bumped the service to 2.1.0 and aligned the OpenAPI spec version.

2026-02-09
- Added root-level version.py for service metadata and container tagging.
- Updated CD workflow to use the Python Docker build workflow.
- Refreshed README with current endpoints and setup steps.
- Updated .gitignore to exclude general .log files but include CHANGELOG.log.
- Created .flaskenv with development environment configuration.

2026-02-01
- Initial repository setup.
